with source as (

    select *
    from "olist_dw"."raw"."customers_dataset"

),

cleaned as (

    select
        customer_id,
        customer_unique_id,
        lpad(customer_zip_code_prefix::text, 5, '0') as customer_zip_code_prefix, -- to keep the zipcodes that starts with zero
        initcap(trim(customer_city)) as customer_city,
        upper(trim(customer_state)) as customer_state

    from source

)

select * from cleaned

with source as (
    select *
    from "olist_dw"."raw"."order_payments_dataset"
),

payments as (
    select
        order_id,
        payment_sequential,
        lower(payment_type) as payment_type,
        payment_installments,
        payment_value
    from source
)

select * from payments

with raw_geo as (
    select
        lpad(geolocation_zip_code_prefix::text, 5, '0') as geolocation_zip_code_prefix,
        geolocation_lat,
        geolocation_lng,
        initcap(geolocation_city) as geolocation_city,
        upper(geolocation_state) as geolocation_state
    from "olist_dw"."raw"."geolocation_dataset"
)

select * from raw_geo

with source as (
    select *
    from "olist_dw"."raw"."order_items_dataset"
),

cleaned as (
    select
        order_id,
        order_item_id,
        product_id,
        seller_id,
        cast(shipping_limit_date as timestamp) as shipping_limit_ts,
        cast(price as numeric) as price,
        cast(freight_value as numeric) as freight_value
    from source
)

select * from cleaned

with source as (
